title: A Review of Episode MMA 50 Michael Bisbing
description:
Bisbing is a former UFC world champion and has the most fights in UFC history. He’s a true champion, super tough fighter and all around great guy. He’s now one of the analysts on Fox for the UFC. This was a great podcast to review. I’ve wanted to know more about Bisbing’s story for some time.

Enjoy my review folks!
